$ System.Management.Automation.ParameterMetadata (class)

`System.Management.Automation.ParameterMetadata` provides information about a → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/function/parameters[Function parameter].

sa:

  Two examples that rudimentarly show how `ParameterMetadata` might be used are:
    • → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/command/get#get-command-query-meta-info
    • → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/function/parameters#ps-param-desc
